WEBVTT

NOTE
Faithful transcript of the narration in the Evolus-produced Evolysse film
(machine-drafted, operator-verified — docs/DECISIONS.md 2026-07-21).

00:00.000 --> 00:04.320
This is Mobile Aesthetics in Harrisburg.
The industry is looking to the future of filler,

00:04.320 --> 00:09.120
and the future is Evolysse. Soften smile lines
with two hyaluronic acid gels designed to make

00:09.120 --> 00:12.880
you look more like you. Smooth moderate to
severe dynamic facial lines with Evolysse.

00:12.880 --> 00:15.520
Tell your doctor if you have a history of
scarring or are taking medicines that decrease

00:15.520 --> 00:18.560
your body's immune response or that can prolong
bleeding. Common side effects include injection

00:18.560 --> 00:22.960
site redness, swelling, pain, tenderness,
lumps, bruising, discoloration, or itching.

00:22.960 --> 00:27.920
As with all fillers, there is a rare risk of
unintentional injection into a blood vessel which
can cause vision abnormalities, blindness,

00:27.920 --> 00:29.920
stroke, temporary scabs, or scarring.
